name: test for get item
query:
select 
				
                parent.variant_of,
				parent.parentfield,
				parent.item_code,
                parent.item_name,
                parent.description,
                parent.net_weight,
                parent.weight_measuring_unit,
                parent.greigh_weight,
                parent.total_parent_qty
				

				
				from  `tabSales Order Item` as parent
				
                where
					parent.parent = "SAL-ORD-2024-00033" and parentfield = "parent_items_table"
